{"tid":950682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錢家有道: 銀紙落得快，肯定有古怪。。。","createTime":"2018-12-21T17:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T17:50:08.000Z","uid":100871,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3de09e47d6e677bebb5f798fd777c5383bcb480c","tid":950682,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thechinfamilyhk/posts/1931600366961235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthechinfamilyhk%2Fposts%2F1931600366961235&d=pWRanps2weUGMQ9AXhniRE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8f2688b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thechinfamilyhk/posts/1931600366961235</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/48373937_1931600133627925_5396625612855050240_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=707df15e14249f62c8ea41cb7bef2ca8&amp;oe=5C8CC216\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F48373937_1931600133627925_5396625612855050240_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D707df15e14249f62c8ea41cb7bef2ca8%26oe%3D5C8CC216&h=7e7fd0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【銀紙滿天飛，唔通係奇蹟？】<br />\n錢生我做咗咁多年人，覺得邊有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳！尤其係有關錢銀嘅嘢，一定要提高警覺，大家記得要 #信定唔信 #睇真啲先好信！<br />\n即上錢家騙案專頁 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2BpeVwh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BpeVwh&d=pWRanps2weUGMQ9AXhniRE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3107358e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2BpeVwh</a> ，睇清投資騙局！<br />\n<br />\nHail of bank notes falling from the sky...... Could it be a miracle? But Mr Chin knows very well that it doesn&rsquo;t pay to be greedy. We have to stay alert to any possible scams. To trust or not to trust? Look carefully before you trust! Let&rsquo;s check out <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Bq4nxe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Bq4nxe&d=pWRanps2weUGMQ9AXhniRE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2